sudo git clone https:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//github.com/nielsbasjes/BugreportRAT362 foo
&lt;/span&gt;sudo chmod -R a+rwx foo
cd foo
mvn -X validate
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;... which will fail on the foo.md closer to the root, instead of the one deeper in the hierarchy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
